    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 1; opacity: 0.04; pointer-events: none; inset: 0; background: var(--texture-grain)\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:72px 44px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid #263223;border-radius:16px;padding:22px 20px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5B9349;background:#5B934918;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:8px;\">CORE DEFINITION</span>\n            <h2 style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#EBF0EA;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1.1;\">The Builder&#x27;s Journey</h2>\n            <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-style:italic;color:#C9D0C7;margin-bottom:12px;opacity:0.8;\">/\u00f0\u0259 \u02c8b\u026ald\u0259rz \u02c8d\u0292\u025c\u02d0rni/</div>\n            <div style=\"border-left:3px solid #5B9349;padding-left:14px;margin:12px 0 14px;\">\n            <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#EBF0EA;margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">Every product that matters was built by someone who almost quit. The difference between shipped and abandoned is one more day of showing up.</p>\n        </div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:10.5px;color:#C9D0C7;margin:0;line-height:1.4;opacity:0.85;\">If you&#x27;re building something and it feels impossible, you&#x27;re exactly where every meaningful project starts.</p>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
